OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, this becoming heavy
OL,7,Fand persistent in the north and west
OL,8,Flater. Windy night with fresh to
OL,9,Fstrong southwesterly winds, gales over
OL,10,Fcoasts and hills later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FHeavy rain in the morning
OL,13,Fclearing to sunny spells and a few
OL,14,Fshowers in the afternoon. Windy at
OL,15,Ffirst.
